summary: An ENB that looks looks great and performs well.
descriptionHtml:
Hi I'm Lexi, I made an ENB! It's not just pretty performance friendly, but also very pretty! I use it myself, since of course I made it. Enjoy!!  :) There is a readme in the files on how to install and uninstall. 

[b][i]I use Vivid Weathers and Realistic Water Two, I highly recommend! Along with , ENBSeries, Particle Patch and Subsurface Scattering Patch http://enbseries.enbdev.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=1499 :) 


[/i][/b]
author: cavity75
